window.bookSummaryJSON = "A little boy receives a toy rabbit for Christmas one year, and he and his plush plaything soon become best friends, embarking on imaginary adventures for hours at a time. When the boy and the rabbit are separated, the toy ventures out on its own to learn about this strange thing \"being real\". This is a heart-warming classic about the great joys of childhood and the magic of love."; 
